    "data": "بِسْمِ ٱللَّهِ ٱلرَّحْمَٰنِ ٱلرَّحِيمِ\nIn the name of Allah, the Beneficent, the Merciful.\nإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ ٱنفَطَرَتْ (1)\nWhen the heaven becomes cleft asunder,\nوَإِذَا ٱلْكَوَاكِبُ ٱنتَثَرَتْ (2)\nAnd when the stars become dispersed,\nوَإِذَا ٱلْبِحَارُ فُجِّرَتْ (3)\nAnd when the seas are made to flow forth,\nوَإِذَا ٱلْقُبُورُ بُعْثِرَتْ (4)\nAnd when the graves are laid open,\nعَلِمَتْ نَفْسٌ مَّا قَدَّمَتْ وَأَخَّرَتْ (5)\nEvery soul shall know what it has sent before and held back.\nيَٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلْإِنسَٰنُ مَا غَرَّكَ بِرَبِّكَ ٱلْكَرِيمِ (6)\nO man! what has beguiled you from your Lord, the Gracious one,\nٱلَّذِى خَلَقَكَ فَسَوَّىٰكَ فَعَدَلَكَ (7)\nWho created you, then made you complete, then made you symmetrical?\nفِىٓ أَىِّ صُورَةٍ مَّا شَآءَ رَكَّبَكَ (8)\nInto whatever form He pleased He constituted you.\nكَلَّا بَلْ تُكَذِّبُونَ بِٱلدِّينِ (9)\nNay! but you give the lie to the judgment day,\nوَإِنَّ عَلَيْكُمْ لَحَٰفِظِينَ (10)\nAnd most surely there are keepers over you\nكِرَامًا كَٰتِبِينَ (11)\nHonorable recorders,\nي��عْلَمُونَ مَا تَفْعَلُونَ (12)\nThey know what you do.\nإِنَّ ٱلْأَبْرَارَ لَفِى نَعِيمٍ (13)\nMost surely the righteous are in bliss,\nوَإِنَّ ٱلْفُجَّارَ لَفِى جَحِيمٍ (14)\nAnd most surely the wicked are in burning fire,\nيَصْلَوْنَهَا يَوْمَ ٱلدِّينِ (15)\nThey shall enter it on the day of judgment.\nوَمَا هُمْ عَنْهَا بِغَآئِبِينَ (16)\nAnd they shall by no means be absent from it.\nوَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا يَوْمُ ٱلدِّينِ (17)\nAnd what will make you realize what the day of judgment is?\nثُمَّ مَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا يَوْمُ ٱلدِّينِ (18)\nAgain, what will make you realize what the day of judgment is?\nيَوْمَ لَا تَمْلِكُ نَفْسٌ لِّنَفْسٍ شَيْـًٔا وَٱلْأَمْرُ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلَّهِ (19)\nThe day on which no soul shall control anything for (another) soul; and the command on that day shall be entirely Allah's.", 
    "title": "82: Al-Infitaar الإنفطار"
}